  "title": "Physiotherapist ( Full Time/Part Time ) #HVN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>·        Conduct thorough patient assessments</p><p>·        Acquiring knowledge and putting a care plan into action to help patients manage their pain and/or disability and restore or enhance their functional capacities.</p><p>·        Inform patients on their condition, methods for self-management and for injury prevention</p><p>·        Track patient development, record results, and modify treatment regimens as necessary.</p><p>·        Work well together with doctors, nurses, and other medical specialists to provide patients with complete treatment.</p><p>·        In compliance with the principles set forth by the Singapore Physiotherapy Association (SPA), uphold a high standard of professionalism and patient care.</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong>:</p><p>·        Bachelor’s Degree in Physiotherapy</p><p>·        Registration with the Singapore Physiotherapy Board.</p><p>·        Minimum 2 years of experience</p><p>·        Ability to work independently and as part of a team.</p><p>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>EA Personnel: Valerie Yong Kian Fung</p><p>CEI No.: R1103704</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</p>",
